createConfigurationSnapshot(string,addre.details: Generates a markdown compatible snapshot of the whole pool configuration into `/reports`.

params.reportName: filename suffix for the generated reports.

defaultTest(string,address,address).details: runs the default test suite that should run on any proposal touching the aave protocol which includes: - diffing the config - checking if the changes are plausible (no conflicting config changes etc) - running an e2e testsuite over all assets

e2eTest(address).details: Makes a e2e test including withdrawals/borrows and supplies to various reserves.

params.pool: the pool that should be tested
